item.title: So you got placed into Woodward Buildings? Here’s what you can expect
item.author: Joe Fletcher,
item.description: odward. The 19-story Imperial flagship built on the outer edge of zone 2, between Acton cemetery, Park Royal industrial estate, and the A40 arterial road. At £128 a week it boasts great facilities for a fraction of the price of the South Kensington Halls. However, for many like myself, it was not …
